---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
---

<Layout title="Inicio" active="home">
    <header>
        <Header/>
        <div class="max-w-[90%] md:max-w-[75%] mx-auto text-center mt-20 justify-center items-center">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl mt-10 uppercase text-[--accent-color]">Planifica tus reuniones y viajes en grupo de forma simple y organizada.</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-[90%] md:max-w-[55%] mx-auto">
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-center mt-12 text-[--subtitles-color]">Con Planify, organiza actividades, divide gastos y explora nuevas opciones, todo en un solo lugar.</h3>
        </div>
        <section class="mx-auto gap-x-5 flex flex-col md:flex-row w-[90%] md:w-[45%] mt-8 justify-center items-center text-sm md:text-base">
            <img class="mx-auto hidden md:block md:w-[50%] h-auto" src="/img/movil-planify.png" alt="Planify Logo"/>

            <div class="w-full md:max-w-[50%] mt-10 md:mt-0">
                <div class="w-fit mx-auto md:mb-10 mb-8">
                    <Button mobileButton fullOpacity hoverScale href="https://planify.eduni.dev/downloads" width="px-8 py-4" fontSize="text-9xl uppercase md:text-5xl">
                        <div class="inline-flex gap-x-0.5">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="24" height="24">
                                <path d="M15.079 5.999l.239 .012c1.43 .097 3.434 1.013 4.508 2.586a1 1 0 0 1 -.344 1.44c-.05 .028 -.372 .158 -.497 .217a4.15 4.15 0 0 0 -.722 .431c-.614 .461 -.948 1.009 -.942 1.694c.01 .885 .339 1.454 .907 1.846c.208 .143 .436 .253 .666 .33c.126 .043 .426 .116 .444 .122a1 1 0 0 1 .662 .942c0 2.621 -3.04 6.381 -5.286 6.381c-.79 0 -1.272 -.091 -1.983 -.315l-.098 -.031c-.463 -.146 -.702 -.192 -1.133 -.192c-.52 0 -.863 .06 -1.518 .237l-.197 .053c-.575 .153 -.964 .226 -1.5 .248c-2.749 0 -5.285 -5.093 -5.285 -9.072c0 -3.87 1.786 -6.92 5.286 -6.92c.297 0 .598 .045 .909 .128c.403 .107 .774 .26 1.296 .508c.787 .374 .948 .44 1.009 .44h.016c.03 -.003 .128 -.047 1.056 -.457c1.061 -.467 1.864 -.685 2.746 -.616l-.24 -.012z"></path>
                                <path d="M14 1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1a3 3 0 0 1 -3 3a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1a3 3 0 0 1 3 -3z"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="24" height="24" stroke-width="2">
                                <path d="M4 10l0 6"></path>
                                <path d="M20 10l0 6"></path>
                                <path d="M7 9h10v8a1 1 0 0 1 -1 1h-8a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1v-8a5 5 0 0 1 10 0"></path>
                                <path d="M8 3l1 2"></path>
                                <path d="M16 3l-1 2"></path>
                                <path d="M9 18l0 3"></path>
                                <path d="M15 18l0 3"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        Descargar Planify
                    </Button>
                </div>
                <p><span class="text-[--accent-color] font-bold">Desde el equipo de Planify</span>, nos esforzamos por ofrecer una plataforma de planificación que sea <span class="text-[--accent-color] font-bold">fácil de usar</span>
                    y que permita a los usuarios <span class="text-[--accent-color] font-bold">planificar sus actividades con facilidad.</span></p>
                <p>Con Planify, puedes <span class="text-[--accent-color] font-bold">planificar tus actividades, gestionar tus gastos y ahorrar dinero</span> en todo momento.
                    <span class="text-[--accent-color] font-bold">¡Empieza a planificar hoy mismo!</span></p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-[90%] md:max-w-[55%] mx-auto pb-40 mt-8 md:mt-16 text-[--text-color] text-sm md:text-base">
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-[--subtitles-color] mb-6">¿Por qué elegir Planify?</h3>
        <p class="mt-5 pl-2 md:pl-8">La herramienta definitiva para <span class="text-[--accent-color] font-bold">organizar y disfrutar tus planes en grupo</span>.</p>
        <ul class="pl-7 md:pl-20 list-inside mt-5 flex flex-col gap-y-4">
            <li class="inline-flex"><svg class="md:size-5 size-9 text-[--principal-color]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M11.5 21h-5.5a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-12a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v4.5"></path>
                <path d="M16 3v4"></path>
                <path d="M8 3v4"></path>
                <path d="M4 11h16"></path>
                <path d="M18 18m-3 0a3 3 0 1 0 6 0a3 3 0 1 0 -6 0"></path>
                <path d="M20.2 20.2l1.8 1.8"></path>
            </svg>Organización fácil con <span class="text-[--accent-color] font-bold">calendario y eventos grupales</span>.</li>
            <li class="inline-flex"><svg class="md:size-5 size-9 text-[--principal-color]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M4 19a2 2 0 1 0 4 0a2 2 0 0 0 -4 0"></path>
                <path d="M13 17h-7v-14h-2"></path>
                <path d="M6 5l14 1l-.575 4.022m-4.925 2.978h-8.5"></path>
                <path d="M21 15h-2.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 0 3h1a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 0 3h-2.5"></path>
                <path d="M19 21v1m0 -8v1"></path>
            </svg><span class="text-[--accent-color] font-bold">Gestión de gastos</span> y compras con un sistema de presupuesto.</li>
            <li class="inline-flex"><svg class="md:size-5 size-9 text-[--principal-color]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M14.5 6.5l3 -2.9a2.05 2.05 0 0 1 2.9 2.9l-2.9 3l2.5 7.5l-2.5 2.55l-3.5 -6.55l-3 3v3l-2 2l-1.5 -4.5l-4.5 -1.5l2 -2h3l3 -3l-6.5 -3.5l2.5 -2.5l7.5 2.5z"></path>
            </svg>Planificación de<span class="text-[--accent-color] font-bold"> viajes y reuniones</span>.</li>
            <li class="inline-flex"><svg class="md:size-5 size-9 text-[--principal-color]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M14 3v4a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h4"></path>
                <path d="M17 21h-10a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-14a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h7l5 5v11a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2z"></path>
                <path d="M12 14h-3"></path>
                <path d="M14 11.172a3 3 0 1 0 0 5.656"></path>
            </svg><span class="text-[--accent-color] font-bold">División de gastos</span> equitativa o personalizada.</li>
            <li class="inline-flex"><svg class="md:size-5 ml-2 size-9 text-[--principal-color]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M8 9h8"></path>
                <path d="M8 13h6"></path>
                <path d="M18 4a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v8a3 3 0 0 1 -3 3h-5l-5 3v-3h-2a3 3 0 0 1 -3 -3v-8a3 3 0 0 1 3 -3h12z"></path>
            </svg>Comunicación fluida con <span class="text-[--accent-color] font-bold">chat integrado</span>.</li>
            <li class="inline-flex"><svg class="md:size-5 size-9 text-[--principal-color]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M12 18.5l-3 -1.5l-6 3v-13l6 -3l6 3l6 -3v7.5"></path>
                <path d="M9 4v13"></path>
                <path d="M15 7v5.5"></path>
                <path d="M21.121 20.121a3 3 0 1 0 -4.242 0c.418 .419 1.125 1.045 2.121 1.879c1.051 -.89 1.759 -1.516 2.121 -1.879z"></path>
                <path d="M19 18v.01"></path>
            </svg><span class="text-[--accent-color] font-bold">Mapa interactivo</span> para puntos de encuentro.</li>
            <li class="inline-flex"><svg class="md:size-5 size-9 text-[--principal-color]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M15.5 13a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -3.5 3.5v1a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 7 0v-1.8"></path>
                <path d="M8.5 13a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 3.5 3.5v1a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 -7 0v-1.8"></path>
                <path d="M17.5 16a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 -7h-.5"></path>
                <path d="M19 9.3v-2.8a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -7 0"></path>
                <path d="M6.5 16a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 -7h.5"></path>
                <path d="M5 9.3v-2.8a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 7 0v10"></path>
            </svg>Inteligencia artificial para <span class="text-[--accent-color] font-bold">recomendaciones turísticas</span>.</li>
            <li class="inline-flex"><svg class="md:size-5 size-9 text-[--principal-color]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M15 8h.01"></path>
                <path d="M10 21h-4a3 3 0 0 1 -3 -3v-12a3 3 0 0 1 3 -3h12a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v5"></path>
                <path d="M3 16l5 -5c.928 -.893 2.072 -.893 3 0l1 1"></path>
                <path d="M14 21v-4a2 2 0 1 1 4 0v4"></path>
                <path d="M14 19h4"></path>
                <path d="M21 15v6"></path>
            </svg><span class="text-[--accent-color] font-bold">Gestión de gastos</span> con tickets e imágenes.</li>
        </ul>
    </main>
</Layout>
